ul.li:
Pending: processing is still going on.
                {
  "result": "Pending",
  "status": "OK"
}

Completed: processing has finished. If the process produces any data, it is
                placed in the 'data' field.
                {
  "result": "Completed",
  "data": {
    "imported": "57678"
  },
  "status": "OK"
}
